node.text: Some real feelings for some real mountains ⛰!
Beautiful scenery in Salzburg! The bridge to Mozart’s home 🏠
Salzburg was an amazing place. I got to meet very nice people who has inspired me a lot. This is why I wanna travel. I will never forget the memories I made here.
Tegernsee was just a paradise! A blue lake laying between the mountains in eastern Germany 🇩🇪. Who would expect! Would you take a dive?
Enjoying German city life with this beauty! We are long gone from Frankfurt but the pics are crisp so need to share! Right now we are near the Tegernsee can’t wait to share those pictures!

I’ve always had a dream of traveling. My mom encouraged me to do so. Explore, meet new people, make memories with the people you love. See beyond your own town because there’s so much more life outside.  We often forget what’s out there being stuck in this digital world. Me myself as well. But right now even traveling near home just brings the most out of me. I truly feel blessed and happy to be able to ride around the world and explore. Be blessed to be able to move. Go outside and live!
